node.text: Bachelorettes in Quarantine 😂 We made this video months ago when the lockdown first began but kept it in the vault to celebrate the start of @clarecrawley journey! Incredibly proud to be a part of this group of brave, beautiful, kind, funny, and inspiring women! Heres to adding a new sister TONIGHT!! 🌹❤️ @tristasutter @schefftwaterman @deannastag @jillian.harris @alifedotowsky @ashleylynnrosenbaum @emilygmaynard @desireesiegfried @andidorfman @kaitlynbristowe @therachlindsay @bkoof @hannahbrown

#VenmoPartner Finally catching a break after these last few weeks and getting some much needed R&R before the craziness starts up again — whew! With such busy schedules, we are constantly looking for ways to work smarter, not harder like using @venmo to help take care of all of the amazing people (contractors, family, tenants, etc...it takes a village) in our lives. Venmo is SO easy to use and to prove it, I’ve partnered up with them. 🤗 Use the link in my bio to download and sign up now. All NEW users who use my link can get $10 in their account! 

Comment your Venmo handle below & let me know how you would use Venmo in any of your summer bucket list plans! ;) Offer ends 8/31/2021. Terms apply; https://bit.ly/JoelleFletcher10

node.text:
If you’re anything like me...you probably have too much stuff 😅 and if you were looking for a sign it’s time to sell … this is it, bc National Garage Sale Day is ALMOST HERE!! 
 
SO excited to partner with @Mercari to declutter my space and sell some unused goods! Trust me y’all, you will feel SO GOOD once you clean out that messy space that’s probably just haunting you atm. 🤣 So now it’s your turn! & To help you create your dream space afterwards, enter the #MercariLocalSweepstakes where one lucky winner will get $3500 plus some fun personal room makeover tips from meeee! 🙋‍♀️ 
 
Check out my IG stories to see how you can enter the sweepstakes and keep an eye out for a few things I’m selling later this week! 😍 #MercariPartner #ad
